- Hearing about how the hill to the right of the town provides free bikes, 
Min heads to biking hill

- After getting there, he meets Steve, who tells asks him "who in their right
minds would be giving bikes out for free?"

- Min fights with Steve, hoping to get a bike

- Win or lose, Min does not get a bike

- Steve tells him to just walk up the hill instead, there's no real reason
you'd need a bike in the first place

- Min walks up the hill, and sees a huge tower and a mountain range in front of him
and curses under his breath